snippet.title: Kingdom Draw Promo
snippet.description:
Kingdom Draw is a free-to-play hybrid of challenging turn-based strategy and customizable card collection gameplay set in a medieval fantasy universe.

Available on:
Steam: PC, MAC, & Linux
Google Play: Android and Chromebooks
Apple AppStore: iPad and iPhone

Website: https://www.kingdom-draw.com
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/46ZYD7SB4P
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/kingdom_draw
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/KingdomDrawGame
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/KingdomDraw/

#KingdomDraw #indiegame 

Developed by Eternal Technics
